MatchedRegions.transcript: Firstly, we verify that most concepts had little effects on the output, which verify the sparsity of encoded concepts.

MatchedRegions.transcript: This is a distinctive property of symbolism, where it is sufficient to use a small number of explicit symbolic concepts to represent the knowledge.

MatchedRegion.Text: The DNN's inference on a specific sample is supposed to be concisely explained by a small number of salient concepts, rather than a large number of concepts.

MatchedRegions.transcript: Such a concept emergent phenomenon has also been mathematically proved in our recent work.

MatchedRegion.Text: Actually, in our recent work [Ren et al., 2023], we have mathematically proved the above sparse concept emerging phenomenon.
